 Conclusion
The Cell Culture Monitoring Biosensor Market is poised for significant growth, driven by the increasing complexity of cell-based research and the growing demand for biopharmaceuticals. Innovations in technology and expanding applications across industries will continue to shape the market, making it an essential segment in the biotechnology sector.

